 580:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal.c ****                                        ##### HAL VREFBUF Control functions #####
 581:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal.c ****  ==================================================================================================
