 718:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal.c **** /**
 719:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal.c ****   * @brief  Enables the VDD I/Os Compensation Cell.
